1. *Odvešću* te na večeru sutra. (I will take you out for dinner tomorrow.)
2. Sutra ujutru *odvešću* decu u školu. (Tomorrow morning I will take the kids to school.)
3. Nadam se da ćeš se složiti da te *odvedem* u bioskop. (I hope you will agree to let me take you to the cinema.)
4. Ako mi *odvedeš* kola na servis, platiću ti ručak. (If you take my car for service, I will buy you lunch.)
5. *Odvedi* psa u šetnju pre nego što padne mrak. (Take the dog for a walk before it gets dark.)
6. Spremna sam da *odvedem* roditelje na aerodrom kada budu išli na put. (I am ready to take my parents to the airport when they travel.)
7. Očekujem da će me *odvesti* na sastanak u njihovoj kancelariji. (I expect them to take me to a meeting in their office.)
8. *Odvela* sam sina kod lekara jer je imao temperaturu. (I took my son to the doctor because he had a fever.)
9. Bilo bi dobro da mi *odvedeš* mamu kod tetke dok se ne vratim sa posla. (It would be great if you could take my mom to my aunt's house while I'm at work.)
10. Planiram da *odvedem* dečka na izlet sledećeg vikenda. (I am planning to take my boyfriend on a trip next weekend.)